Website: Check out @user5. It seems simple, looks good, and is OpenSource. I'll be switching one of my websites to it before the next renewal.
Signal: Check out cal.com. It's an Open-Source calendar service with integrations that allow you to plan video calls with Element Call, JITSI, etc. Signal is also supported, but I haven't tried it yet to see if it's for messages or video.
I can recommend @user6. E2EE, decentralized, Open Source.
